366
00:35:05,254 --> 00:35:07,395
Retrocedendo a câmera um.

367
00:35:09,277 --> 00:35:12,061
Jesus, quem rouba um dedo?

368
00:35:12,161 --> 00:35:13,828
Oh, sim.

369
00:35:13,928 --> 00:35:15,995
Oh, porra.

370
00:35:16,095 --> 00:35:18,433
